{"id":141333,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/twitter-创始人biz-stone：绝不会放弃中国市场/","date":"2011-03-25T17:00:22Z","modified":"2011-03-25T17:00:22Z","title":"Twitter 创始人Biz Stone：绝不会放弃中国市场","content":"<p><p><a rel=\"attachment wp-att-19072\" href=\"http://www.36kr.com/twitter-wont-ignore-china/twitter_block/\"><img title=\"twitter_block\" src=\"http://www.36kr.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/twitter_block-300x290.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"290\" /></a></p>\n<p>Twitter 联合创始人Biz Stone 在周四的CTIA 展会上<a href=\"http://www.pcworld.com/article/223233/\">表示</a>，Twitter 绝对不会放弃中国市场，只是目前还不会立刻采取行动解决此事。Stone 称，“信息的自由交换将是未来的趋势”，大家应该去适应这个趋势，而不是抵制它。</p>\n<p>目前，中国市场的微博发展非常迅速，据传新浪微博用户已经超过1亿。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.pcworld.com/article/223233/\">via</a></p>\n<div>\n<p><strong>转载请注明：</strong> “转载自<a href=\"http://www.36kr.com/twitter-wont-ignore-china/\">@36氪</a>”，<strong>谢谢:)</strong></p>\n</div>\n<p><div>\n<b>感谢<a href=\"http://www.1space.org/\">壹号空间</a>赞助@36氪 主机服务</b>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p>我要分享到：</p>\n<p>\t<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://v.t.sina.com.cn/share/share.php?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.36kr.com%2Ftwitter-wont-ignore-china%2F&#038;title=@36%E6%B0%AA%C2%BB%20Twitter%20%E5%88%9B%E5%A7%8B%E4%BA%BABiz%20Stone%EF%BC%9A%E7%BB%9D%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E6%94%BE%E5%BC%83%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA&#038;content=utf-8\" title=\"新浪微博\"><img src=\"http://www.36kr.com/wp-content/plugins/sociable/images/sina.png\" title=\"新浪微博\" alt=\"新浪微博\" /></a><br />\n\t<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://share.renren.com/share/buttonshare.do?link=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.36kr.com%2Ftwitter-wont-ignore-china%2F&#038;title=Twitter%20%E5%88%9B%E5%A7%8B%E4%BA%BABiz%20Stone%EF%BC%9A%E7%BB%9D%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E6%94%BE%E5%BC%83%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA\" title=\"人人\"><img src=\"http://www.36kr.com/wp-content/plugins/sociable/images/renren.png\" title=\"人人\" alt=\"人人\" /></a><br />\n\t<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.douban.com/recommend/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.36kr.com%2Ftwitte